    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Works, in any medium, in which the primary or only subject is the human figure or figures. Used especially when no other iconography is depicted.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
